  <text xml:space="preserve">
    <body>
      <div type="edition" xml:lang="okz-Latn">
        <p>
                      <lb n="1"/><g type="circleTarget">.</g> vraḥ vleṅ· svargga
                   </p>
        <lg met="upajāti" n="1" xml:lang="san-Latn">
          <l n="a"><lb n="2"/><g type="circleTarget">.</g> Iman divaś śrīmadhurendrasūri<space/>r</l>
          <l n="b">agniṁ patantaṁ samakālam atra</l>
          <l n="c"><lb n="3"/>śrīvīraśaktyāgamanena so 'ha<space/>m</l>
          <l n="d">adrākṣam aṣṭātriśaśāṅkarūpaiḥ <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g></l>
        </lg>
        <lg met="upajāti" n="2" xml:lang="san-Latn">
          <l n="a"><lb n="4"/><g type="circleTarget">.</g> dr̥ṣṭo mayā dīdhitadiṅmukho 'gni<space/>r</l>
          <l n="b">divaḥ patan śrījayavarmmarājye</l>
          <l n="c"><lb n="5"/>Atyadbhutaṁ yatsaphalāni manye <space/></l>
          <l n="d">jātañ ca netre ca kulañ ca me syuḥ <g type="gomutraFinal">.</g></l>
        </lg>
      </div>
      <div type="apparatus">
        <listApp>
          <app loc="4">
            <lem>dīdhitadiṅmukho·</lem>
            <rdg source="bib:Maxwell2009_01">dīpitadiṅmukho</rdg>
          </app>
        </listApp>
      </div>
      <div source="bib:Maxwell2009_01" type="translation">
        <p n="1">The Sacred Fire from heaven.</p>
        <p n="1" rend="stanza">I myself, Śrī-Madhurendrasūri, saw this Fire falling from heaven, here, at the time of the arrival of Śrī-Vīraśakti in 1138 <supplied reason="subaudible">Śaka</supplied>.</p>
        <p n="2" rend="stanza">I have seen the Fire lighting up the directions of space <supplied reason="subaudible">and</supplied> falling from heaven into the kingdom of Śrī-Jayavarman - a great wonder, which I believe will entail good results, <supplied reason="subaudible">namely</supplied> high birth, two <supplied reason="subaudible">good</supplied> eyes, and eminent family. May these be mine!</p>
      </div>
